  "subCategorySlug": "marbling",
  "difficulty": "INTERMEDIATE",
  "season": null,
  "sourceType": "PUBLIC_DOMAIN",
  "sourceNotes": "Josef Halfer, The Progress of the Marbling Art (English translation 1894), chapter on stone patterns. C. W. Woolnough, The Art of Marbling (1881 edition). Both public domain. Both sources describe the bouquet base and stone-modification technique.",
